"Tutorial.DataTypes> greet dr \"Höck\"\n"
"\"Hello, Dr. Höck!\"\n"
"Tutorial.DataTypes> greet Mrs \"Smith\"\n"
"\"Hello, Mrs. Smith!\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/DataTypes.md:400
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Data types like `Title` are called *sum types* as they consist\n"
