#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/Tutorial/DPair.md:763
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Fail early: With the exception of the command parser, all functions updating the table and handling queries should be typed and implemented in such a way that they cannot fail."
