#. type: Fenced code block (repl)
#: ../src/Tutorial/Functor.md:1167
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Tutorial.Functor> decodeCRUD {i = Nat} {a = Email} 1 \"Create,jon@doe.ch\"\n"
