"print2 : (impl : Print a) => a -> String\n"
"print2 = print' impl\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Predicates.md:1120
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"As yet another alternative, we could use the syntax for auto\n"
"implicit arguments:\n"
