#. type: Bullet: '2. '
#: ../src/Tutorial/Traverse.md:458
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Ability to communicate the updated state to later stateful computations. In case of a pure function this means, that the function will return a pair of values: The computation's result plus the updated state."
