#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Traverse.md:462
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"These two prerequisites lead to the following generic\n"
"type for a pure, stateful computation operating on state\n"
"type `st` and producing values of type `a`:\n"
